    "body" : "<pre><code>Thread t1 = new Thread(new Runnable() {\n    @Override\n    public void run() {\n        // code goes here.\n    }\n});  \nt1.start();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>new Thread(new Runnable() {\n     @Override\n     public void run() {\n          // code goes here.\n     }\n}).start();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>new Thread(() -&gt; {\n    // code goes here.\n}).start();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>Executors.newSingleThreadExecutor().execute(new Runnable() {\n    @Override\n    public void run() {\n        myCustomMethod();\n    }\n});\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or </p>\n\n<pre><code>Executors.newCachedThreadPool().execute(new Runnable() {\n    @Override\n    public void run() {\n        myCustomMethod();\n    }\n});\n</code></pre>\n"
