    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In java 8 you can call it through method reference by creating new thread.</p>\n<pre><code>Thread t = new Thread(new YourClassName::doWork);\nt.start();\n</code></pre>\n<p>you can refer static mathod also, in that case you don't need to use new operator.</p>\n"
